    <item>
      <title>印度大型债券基金认为长期利率正在下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/india-s-big-bond-funds-argue-that-long-term-rates-are-going-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度一些最大的债券基金经理表示，该国利率将长期下降，这将为 1.3 万亿美元的政府债务市场带来新的投资时代。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/india-s-big-bond-funds-argue-that-long-term-rates-are-going-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利总理梅洛尼誓言在“一带一路”遭冷遇后恢复与中国的联系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-29/italy-s-meloni-vows-to-renew-china-ties-after-belt-and-road-snub</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利总理乔治娅·梅洛尼在首次正式访问北京之际承诺重启与中国的双边合作。意大利去年退出了中国的“一带一路”倡议。彭博电视台记者刘敏敏报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-29/italy-s-meloni-vows-to-renew-china-ties-after-belt-and-road-snub</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 00:55:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟意外拒绝阿尔茨海默症药物，卫材股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/eisai-shares-sink-on-surprise-eu-rejection-of-alzheimer-s-drug</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧洲药品监管机构拒绝了卫材与 Biogen Inc. 联合开发的阿尔茨海默氏症治疗药物后，卫材股价下跌逾 12%，为三年来最大跌幅，这可能对其全球销售扩张计划造成打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/eisai-shares-sink-on-surprise-eu-rejection-of-alzheimer-s-drug</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 00:43:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着两国关系日益密切，中国投资者纷纷涌入沙特 ETF</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/china-investors-pile-into-saudi-etfs-as-two-nations-grow-closer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于沙特阿拉伯股市的惨淡表现刺激了对海外资产的需求，中国投资者正将资金投入两只跟踪沙特阿拉伯股票的新交易所交易基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/china-investors-pile-into-saudi-etfs-as-two-nations-grow-closer</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 00:22:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
