      <title>油价持于六周低点附近，关注中国需求和 OPEC+</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-29</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在本周 OPEC+ 监测会议召开之前，油价稳定在六周低点附近，因为积极的中国经济数据有助于缓解人们对全球最大进口国的需求的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-29</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 23:31:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市早盘上涨，进入日本央行和美联储周：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/asian-stocks-eye-early-gains-into-boj-fed-week-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日本、美国和英国央行本周将作出重要决策以及一些大型科技公司公布业绩之前，亚洲股市周一结束连续三天的下跌并开始上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-28/asian-stocks-eye-early-gains-into-boj-fed-week-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 22:41:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
